Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:09.71,mazoku - kune,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H496ADB&\pos(1623.999,181.333)}轉學面試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:06.35,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,我們為你準備了課題和小論文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.95,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,然後這是新學期的考試範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:09.89,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.86,mazoku - text,,0,0,0,,我是從這附近來的
